CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 4, 2013

[Cite as 12/04/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5285.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013-1517. State ex rel. Dudley v. Lucas Cty. Court of Common Pleas.

In Prohibition. On motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
